361
00:25:09,784 --> 00:25:11,885
Oh, pivo može. Hvala.

362
00:25:14,489 --> 00:25:16,389
Oh, zdravo, kuco.

363
00:25:16,390 --> 00:25:20,226
- Zove se Sem.
- Zdravo, Sem.

364
00:25:20,227 --> 00:25:22,528
